Step 15: Verify the WAR File

Go to the Jenkins workspace.

cd /var/lib/jenkins/workspace

Open your project.

cd webapp

Go to the target directory.

cd target

List the files.

ls -l

Example output:

webapp.war
classes/
generated-sources/
maven-status/

The .war file is the deployable Java web application artifact generated by Maven.
